        treatment in South Africa.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject must be 18 years of age or older of either gender or race.

          -  Subject must provide informed consent and comply with the survey procedures.

          -  Subject is on lipid lowering drug treatment for at least 3 months, with no dose change
             for a minimum of 6 weeks.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are unwilling or unable to provide informed consent.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
